3.19.20  11:28 am   Help!! I am ready for the big project but am terrified by the myriad aspects to keep track of and don't know how to build up the courage to start. 

     that makes sense. i can tell you what worked for me, which was to do smaller projects for a while, and i was able to learn a lot of useful procedures which worked on bigger projects. it also helps to relentlessly talk things over on audio/video recording, and write things down. ask questions. play 'what do we know'. each tiny answer leads to more answers, it's kind of like a disease spreading, but in this case it's knowledge, and answers
